341
00:30:02,960 --> 00:30:06,680
My shoe...

342
00:30:10,550 --> 00:30:14,520
Move! Move!

343
00:30:27,960 --> 00:30:32,960
♫ I think of you any moment. It gets bigger and bigger ♫

