365
00:33:39,290 --> 00:33:43,130
King Jin Heung, Sam Maek Jong - King of the 24th generation of Silla

366
00:33:46,490 --> 00:33:49,200
Why did you come here?

367
00:34:00,750 --> 00:34:05,540
27th years of King Beop Heung's reign - 11 years ago

368
00:34:11,990 --> 00:34:16,830
Your Highness, His Majesty has passed away.

369
00:34:32,400 --> 00:34:37,320
We have to protect the last Sacred Bone of the kingdowm tonight with whatever it takes. ("Sacred Bone" -- someone of royal lineage maternally and paternally)

370
00:34:37,320 --> 00:34:40,270
