376
00:35:19,930 --> 00:35:23,850
We can't trust any of our soldiers or eunuchs in the palace.

377
00:35:23,850 --> 00:35:27,590
- Do you not know the situation?
- How can I not know?

378
00:35:27,590 --> 00:35:31,280
