386
00:36:04,080 --> 00:36:09,470
I am just checking to see if my throne is doing well.

387
00:36:09,470 --> 00:36:11,680
I merely came to just to check on that.

388
00:36:11,750 --> 00:36:16,850
If I didn't do this, I felt I would have forgotten who I was.

389
00:36:16,880 --> 00:36:19,480
You weak bastard.

390
00:36:20,230 --> 00:36:24,270
