408
00:39:06,040 --> 00:39:09,580
Who knows? I can pay you more than what it's worth!

409
00:39:09,580 --> 00:39:15,900
They said that if I killed a True Bone they'd give me three bags of rice! ( "True Bone" - royalty but not the immediate family of the King)

410
00:39:15,900 --> 00:39:18,270
Three bags of rice?

411
00:39:25,400 --> 00:39:30,770
They'll give you three bags of rice? Did you hear that, Pa Oh?

412
00:39:41,510 --> 00:39:44,250
Are you okay, Your Majesty?

413
00:40:22,160 --> 00:40:26,800
He was an ignorant lad who knew nothing. Did you really have to kill him?

414
00:40:26,800 --> 00:40:28,720
He saw your face.

415
00:40:28,720 --> 00:40:32,680
What kind of man attempts to kill the king for three bags of rice?

