417
00:40:37,020 --> 00:40:39,630
Queen Dowager's command?

418
00:40:40,860 --> 00:40:43,070
Then it can't be helped.

419
00:40:44,010 --> 00:40:47,040
This city is hers.

420
00:40:48,880 --> 00:40:50,630
Your Majesty.

421
00:41:00,980 --> 00:41:02,560
Your Majesty.

