As soon as he met her, he led Na Jeong into the woods

516
00:53:03,870 --> 00:53:08,570
and pushed her against the pine tree, with just his hands!

517
00:53:08,570 --> 00:53:10,980
And that's how...

518
00:53:11,900 --> 00:53:14,420
Because of you...

519
00:53:14,420 --> 00:53:17,300
I'm going to burn up!

520
00:53:19,100 --> 00:53:23,560
The two couldn't restrain themselves and wanted each other's lips.

521
00:53:25,210 --> 00:53:28,810
Finally, without hesitating...

522
00:53:28,810 --> 00:53:30,370
Rip!

523
00:53:34,030 --> 00:53:35,780
Do you know where this is?

524
00:53:35,780 --> 00:53:37,880
You!

525
00:53:41,340 --> 00:53:45,070
Who is doing this at this crucial moment?

526
00:53:46,510 --> 00:53:49,690
It was you? Ban Ryu's trash?

527
00:53:51,320 --> 00:53:53,250
What are you doing right now?

528
00:53:53,250 --> 00:53:55,450
Kang Seong, what is going on?

529
00:53:55,450 --> 00:53:58,750
I can't believe this.

530
00:53:58,750 --> 00:54:01,810
This is the second time I've seen you today.

531
00:54:03,190 --> 00:54:06,170
If you are out of luck, you should have asked for God's blessing at least.

532
00:54:06,170 --> 00:54:09,760
Don't mess with me. Unless you want to go back home with that face.

533
00:54:09,760 --> 00:54:12,730
I ought to...

534
00:54:13,730 --> 00:54:16,470
Prince Soo Ho and Prince Ban Ryu are about to have another fight.

535
00:54:16,470 --> 00:54:19,020
Really? Then I'll have to go watch!

536
00:54:19,020 --> 00:54:22,280
There's no way we can miss this fight.

537
00:54:44,560 --> 00:54:47,090
What did I do to make you close your eyes?

538
00:54:47,090 --> 00:54:50,020
Wh-who are you?

539
00:54:50,020 --> 00:54:54,240
Whoever I am. Is the answer to that question important?

540
00:54:54,820 --> 00:54:57,610
Ah, that's a shame.

541
00:54:57,610 --> 00:54:58,890
It's only been three days.

542
00:54:58,890 --> 00:55:01,850
What... What has?

543
00:55:02,930 --> 00:55:05,040
So, it might be best to open your eyes.

544
00:55:05,040 --> 00:55:07,260
Wh-why are you doing this?

545
00:55:07,260 --> 00:55:09,140
Why, you ask?

546
00:55:09,800 --> 00:55:12,590
Because it's dim here.

547
00:55:14,010 --> 00:55:16,450
And no one is here.

548
00:55:17,580 --> 00:55:19,760
And it's good to sleep here.

549
00:55:25,750 --> 00:55:28,300
How does the next part go?

550
00:55:40,120 --> 00:55:43,180
Ban Ryu, he doesn't even have an entrance pass!

551
00:55:43,180 --> 00:55:47,200
It's not a crime to beat up Cheonin without a transit pass in the capital.
(Cheonin was the lowest rank of Silla society)

552
00:55:47,200 --> 00:55:51,150
So it's okay to kill him, right?

553
00:55:55,910 --> 00:56:00,700
You ignored strict Silla Bone Rank System. ( The system was based on how closely related you were to the king.)

554
00:56:00,700 --> 00:56:04,530
And you dare crawl into a place like this?

555
00:56:05,450 --> 00:56:10,370
People like you are no different from bugs.

556
00:56:12,980 --> 00:56:15,050
Farewell.

557
00:56:20,340 --> 00:56:23,650
Who did that?

558
00:56:38,870 --> 00:56:41,510
What's with that bamboo hat?

559
00:56:47,860 --> 00:56:51,450
I think life is all about luck.

560
00:56:55,960 --> 00:56:58,700
But today,

561
00:56:58,700 --> 00:57:01,040
you are not lucky.

562
00:57:01,040 --> 00:57:03,240
You, what are you?

563
00:57:03,240 --> 00:57:05,870
Bothersome bastard.

564
00:57:06,740 --> 00:57:09,300
I asked you who you are!

565
00:57:09,300 --> 00:57:11,660
There's nothing you need to know.

566
00:57:11,660 --> 00:57:13,730
Are you okay?

567
00:57:14,530 --> 00:57:16,310
♫ Little by little, little by little ♫
Yeah.

568
00:57:16,310 --> 00:57:19,940
♫ Like a withering flower ♫

569
00:57:19,940 --> 00:57:21,630
I am not okay.

570
00:57:21,630 --> 00:57:23,780
Arrogant bastard!

571
00:57:27,210 --> 00:57:30,420
Oh, that was good!

572
00:57:40,900 --> 00:57:44,970
If killing a Cheonin who sneaked into the capital is your law,

573
00:57:44,970 --> 00:57:48,260
my law is to beat up the royals who cross this line.

574
00:57:51,010 --> 00:57:54,280
If you want to cut him, cross the line to do so. I will fight you.

575
00:57:54,280 --> 00:57:59,160
♫ Don't run away. Don't leave me alone ♫

576
00:57:59,160 --> 00:58:04,270
♫ You who are turning away turn your feet toward me ♫

577
00:58:04,270 --> 00:58:09,350
♫ I request and want you, you are everything in my life ♫
